# Git mailmap — corrects historical author attribution for display.
#
# Format: <correct-name> <correct-email> <commit-name> <commit-email>
# Honored by `git log`, `git shortlog`, `git blame`, and GitHub's UI.
# See: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitmailmap
#
# 2026-05-13: A misconfigured global `user.name=Test / user.email=test@test.com`
# was used to author commits before being corrected. Map those back to the
# real author for display. Underlying commit objects are unchanged.

Carlos D. Escobar-Valbuena <carlosdavidescobar@gmail.com> Test <test@test.com>
Carlos D. Escobar-Valbuena <carlosdavidescobar@gmail.com> Carlos Escobar <carlosdavidescobar@gmail.com>
